  "texts": [
    "In summary, MMER-TD (Ours) consistently exhibited superior performance across multiple crucial metrics.",
    "Classification Recognition ResultsTo delve into the confusion matrices of our model across two datasets, refer to Figures 4 and 5.",
    "These matrices display the performance across different classification tasks within the MOSEI dataset.",
    "Confusion matrices are pivotal for assessing the performance of classification models, depicting the relationship between actual and predicted categories.",
    "In Figure 4a for the 3-class classification, most of the true \"0\" labels are correctly predicted as \"0\", indicated Multi-Modal Emotion Recognition Using Tensor Decomposition Fusion and Self-Supe by the darkest area of the matrix, suggesting a majority count."
  ]
